<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-23-1068 </DOCNO><TEXT>Together with the 'Order Emission Demands Burners WLV' a regulation forthe measuring methods came into effect. Dutch companies now have to dealwith control measurements of noxious emissions. Two examples of controlmeasurements are discussed. The first concerns NO/sub x/ emission measurementsat gas turbine installations, the second is particulate emission measurement.5 figs., 1 tab.</TEXT></DOC>